橙，奇異果，蘋果，櫻桃)"},{"pid":"38706129f86fa60693da48da2aa0d1887e9954db","tid":45414,"uid":26672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"地捫西梅汁是皇道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過咪一炮過灌啊，會肚痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f81a1bcf3290341c034c21e6e6853342a8fb96","tid":45414,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T15:49:38.000Z","msg":"火龍果"},{"pid":"3395b930491abee744395bf55fa2d1a5ca3f7214","tid":45414,"uid":51275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經成日食菜同飲水 都係兩三日先屙一次屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要點先可以令肚仔每日變fit啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真回你<br />\n食煙可以柯得好撚暢順<br />\n我大概食左兩年煙 未試過便秘到而家<br />\n<br />\n係食煙前一直都有便秘問題 <br />\n一星期大概柯3-5次屎<br />\n平圴柯半個鐘or over<br />\n經常性柯唔出 ／死谷谷到一半出唔曬／柯屎帶血<br />\n細個飲食唔健康 以為係原因 開始做運動<br />\n亦都有食菜同水果 乳酪類產品亦日日食<br />\n運動做左好耐 無可能係運動不足<br />\n體重由9字頭減到70<br />\n都仲係會便秘 快極都要4個字一joy<br />\n試過柯屎柯到喊<br />\n<br />\n直到有次 係柯到想喊既時候<br />\n諗起朋友話食煙柯屎會好順暢<br />\n跟手拎老豆一枝黎食<br />\n真係爽快過屌你老母<br />\n而家日日柯前食煙or食住柯己經係慣例"},{"pid":"bf0e642ff6f0dcf7dfcc0feed37c485a8163febe","tid":45414,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:51:02.000Z","msg":"每周做兩至三45分鐘以上的帶氧運動，如慢跑，加上飲食均衡就OK"},{"pid":"4799b15474fd400772e3b639d4342858a85b1675","tid":45414,"uid":66203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:34:30.000Z","msg":"我都有便秘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好辛苦 每次feel得有得痾都唔會放過 一定會去廁所坐左先 但好多時都痾唔出 呢排飲苦瓜水同食火龍果 每日都有得痾<br />\n諗緊睇唔睇腸胃科"},{"pid":"7c377f37cb98939ee3008672a8069a46c7cfc5d3","tid":45414,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T11:59:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f96b8eba44d900c508606e8eb63431daf3d175fb","tid":45414,"uid":69091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"食蕉"},{"pid":"823dcd3cb4399b03ad2b4ef4c74fd4e6b98f1f75","tid":45414,"uid":29522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"地捫西梅汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4974020bca48be7f1e37f9b34ede3a5178b8345b","tid":45414,"uid":59922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"乳酪。每次食都即日或者翌日都有得去，明明啲屎有唔少菜葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n其實除咗食菜，仲要飲足夠嘅水。"},{"pid":"db066ae5c0c8c9a9a334eec5b69b0dcfb97b6ec9","tid":45414,"uid":67895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"認真 早晚沖亞麻籽粉飲<br />\n最近淘寶淘左包<br />\n日日有得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5308be41537f724b90cf1dc5f692e8bebf40c66d","tid":45414,"uid":37397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:17:55.000Z","msg":"其實講到底都係情緒病"},{"pid":"cab4eb5d8e2734b3c185a54885c8214a1716260b","tid":45414,"uid":28884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"益生菌"},{"pid":"4fe0db413516d547475fce3f62cdc4d05709b718","tid":45414,"uid":15514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T18:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已經成日食菜同飲水 都係兩三日先屙一次屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要點先可以令肚仔每日變fit啲<img src=\"/assets/fac